CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FA launch event took place in
OL,7,FWadebridge on Friday 24 July during
OL,8,Fwhich representatives from Devon and
OL,9,FCornwall Police explained plans to
OL,10,Ftarget the root causes of violence and
OL,11,Fabuse before harm occurs.
OL,13,FChief Constable James Vaughan said:
OL,14,F"Most violence against women is
OL,15,Fperpetrated by men. But most men are
OL,16,Fgood men. And most boys are good boys.
OL,17,FAnd I want good boys and good men to
OL,18,Fstand up alongside their sisters and
OL,19,Ftheir mothers and strong women to say
OL,20,Fstop and enough is enough."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
