PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FThe Male Ally Network is supported
OL,7,Fthrough #100,000 of investment,
OL,8,Fincluding #50,000 from the Office of
OL,9,Fthe Police and Crime Commissioner and
OL,10,F#50,000 from proceeds of crime funding
OL,11,Fallocated by Chief Constable Vaughan.
OL,13,FHalf of this investment has been taken
OL,14,Fout of the #2.9m of seized assets from
OL,15,Fself-proclaimed misogynist Andrew Tate
OL,16,Fand his brother Tristan, relating to
OL,17,Ftax and VAT evasion and money
OL,18,Flaundering offences.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FResearch shows that attitudes and
OL,7,Fbehaviours which enable violence can
OL,8,Foften go unchallenged. The Male Ally
OL,9,FNetwork aims to encourage participants
OL,10,Fto consider the influence they have as
OL,11,Fcolleagues, friends, teammates,
OL,12,Fleaders, fathers, partners and role
OL,13,Fmodels, and how that influence can
OL,14,Fhelp shape safer and more respectful
OL,15,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FAlexis Bowater from the Male Ally
OL,7,FNetwork said: "I would like to see a
OL,8,Fmale ally in every single sector of
OL,9,Fsociety across Cornwall - in fishing
OL,10,Fcommunities, in pubs, in clubs, on
OL,11,Fconstruction sites..."
OL,13,FMan Culture from Plymouth was one of
OL,14,Fthe groups attending the network
OL,15,Flaunch. Its members already instigate
OL,16,Fconversations with men at events
OL,17,Facross the region to help them
OL,18,Funderstand that the issue of violence
OL,19,Fagainst women and girls is close to
OL,20,Fhome.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
