PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FAndy Hodges explained: "I think the
OL,7,Ffirst conversation you have is with
OL,8,Fyour partner, with your daughter, with
OL,9,Fthe women in your lives, and ask them
OL,10,Fwhat their daily safety feels like."
OL,12,FTruro and Penwith College is among the
OL,13,Fschools already talking to students
OL,14,Fabout these issues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
