PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FSafeguarding Officer Gary Kos said:
OL,7,F"Say, for instance, we have a
OL,8,Fbricklaying student. We try to get one
OL,9,Fof his tutors - somebody he knows, as
OL,10,Fopposed to just another suit, another
OL,11,Fauthority figure coming in with a
OL,12,Fshirt and tie, or a police officer
OL,13,Fcoming in to speak to him - actually,
OL,14,Fwe can do that at a grassroots level."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
