PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FThe programme is funded by the Office
OL,7,Fof the Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,8,Fand Devon & Cornwall Police, with the
OL,9,Fsupport of a Cornwall-based steering
OL,10,Fgroup led by Ambassador for Cornwall
OL,11,FGeraint Richards, former High Sheriff
OL,12,Fof Cornwall, and comprising
OL,13,Frepresentatives from the police as
OL,14,Fwell as Cornwall Council, Barnardo's,
OL,15,FFirst Light, Cornwall Voluntary Sector
OL,16,FForum, The Women's Centre Cornwall and
OL,17,FWest Cornwall Women's Aid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
