PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FCommissioner Hernandez said: "If we
OL,7,Fare serious about ending violence
OL,8,Fagainst women and girls, we need
OL,9,Feveryone to be part of the solution.
OL,11,F"The vast majority of men are not
OL,12,Fperpetrators of violence, but all men
OL,13,Fhave a role to play in challenging
OL,14,Fharmful behaviour and creating
OL,15,Fenvironments where women and girls
OL,16,Ffeel safe and respected.
OL,26,@nD@^OUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
