FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,F"The Male Ally Network is about giving
OL,7,Fpeople the confidence, knowledge and
OL,8,Fsupport to step forward, become
OL,9,Fambassadors for change and influence
OL,10,Fthose around them.
OL,12,F"This launch marks an important step
OL,13,Fin building a movement across Cornwall
OL,14,Fthat recognises preventing violence is
OL,15,Feveryone's responsibility."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
