FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784908087
OL,3,CMale Ally Network launched with call
OL,4,Cfor cultural change to protect women
OL,6,FAmbassador for Cornwall Mr Richards
OL,7,Fsaid: "During my year as High Sheriff
OL,8,Fof Cornwall I became deeply aware of,
OL,9,Fand moved by, the sad reality of the
OL,10,Fnature and extent of violence against
OL,11,Fwomen and girls.
OL,13,F"Through conversations with others the
OL,14,Fidea of a Male Ally Network in
OL,15,FCornwall was developed and I am
OL,16,Fdelighted to see so many people,
OL,17,Frepresenting organisations from across
OL,18,FCornwall, coming together with a
OL,19,Fdetermination to make a positive
OL,20,Fdifference to the lives of women and
OL,21,Fgirls here."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
